// python Phase 1: 기본 패키지 관리
// 목표: 패키지 설치, 목록 조회, 버전 관리

type PackageID = u64
type Timestamp = u64
type PackageName = string
type Version = string

enum PackageStatus {
    Available
    Installed
    Outdated
    Broken
}

type Package {
    id: PackageID
    name: PackageName
    version: Version
    status: PackageStatus
    installed_at: Timestamp
    size: u64
}

type Dependency {
    package_name: PackageName
    required_version: Version
}

type PackageManager {
    packages: Vec<Package>
    installed_packages: Vec<PackageID>
    next_package_id: PackageID
    total_installed_size: u64
}

impl PackageManager {

    fn new() -> PackageManager {
        PackageManager {
            packages: Vec::new(),
            installed_packages: Vec::new(),
            next_package_id: 1000u64,
            total_installed_size: 0u64
        }
    }

    // 패키지 추가 (저장소)
    fn register_package(mut self, name: PackageName, version: Version, size: u64) -> (PackageManager, PackageID) {
        let package_id = self.next_package_id
        self.next_package_id = self.next_package_id + 1u64

        let package = Package {
            id: package_id,
            name: name,
            version: version,
            status: PackageStatus::Available,
            installed_at: 0u64,
            size: size
        }

        self.packages.push(package)
        (self, package_id)
    }

    // 패키지 설치
    fn install(mut self, package_id: PackageID) -> (PackageManager, bool) {
        let mut found = false
        let mut i = 0u64

        while i < self.packages.len() {
            let pkg = self.packages.get(i)

            match pkg {
                Some(p) => {
                    if p.id == package_id {
                        match p.status {
                            PackageStatus::Installed => {
                                found = true
                            }
                            _ => {
                                let updated = Package {
                                    id: p.id,
                                    name: p.name,
                                    version: p.version,
                                    status: PackageStatus::Installed,
                                    installed_at: get_timestamp(),
                                    size: p.size
                                }
                                self.packages.set(i, updated)
                                self.installed_packages.push(package_id)
                                self.total_installed_size = self.total_installed_size + p.size
                                found = true
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
                None => {}
            }

            i = i + 1u64
        }

        (self, found)
    }

    // 패키지 제거
    fn uninstall(mut self, package_id: PackageID) -> (PackageManager, bool) {
        let mut found = false
        let mut i = 0u64

        while i < self.packages.len() {
            let pkg = self.packages.get(i)

            match pkg {
                Some(p) => {
                    if p.id == package_id {
                        let updated = Package {
                            id: p.id,
                            name: p.name,
                            version: p.version,
                            status: PackageStatus::Available,
                            installed_at: 0u64,
                            size: p.size
                        }
                        self.packages.set(i, updated)
                        found = true

                        // installed_packages에서 제거
                        let mut j = 0u64
                        while j < self.installed_packages.len() {
                            let installed_id = self.installed_packages.get(j)
                            match installed_id {
                                Some(id) => {
                                    if id == package_id {
                                        self.total_installed_size = self.total_installed_size - p.size
                                    }
                                }
                                None => {}
                            }
                            j = j + 1u64
                        }
                    }
                }
                None => {}
            }

            i = i + 1u64
        }

        (self, found)
    }

    // 설치된 패키지 목록
    fn list_installed(ref self) -> Vec<(PackageID, PackageName, Version)> {
        let mut result = Vec::new()
        let mut i = 0u64

        while i < self.packages.len() {
            let pkg = self.packages.get(i)

            match pkg {
                Some(p) => {
                    match p.status {
                        PackageStatus::Installed => {
                            result.push((p.id, p.name, p.version))
                        }
                        _ => {}
                    }
                }
                None => {}
            }

            i = i + 1u64
        }

        result
    }

    // 사용 가능한 패키지 목록
    fn list_available(ref self) -> Vec<(PackageID, PackageName, Version)> {
        let mut result = Vec::new()
        let mut i = 0u64

        while i < self.packages.len() {
            let pkg = self.packages.get(i)

            match pkg {
                Some(p) => {
                    match p.status {
                        PackageStatus::Available => {
                            result.push((p.id, p.name, p.version))
                        }
                        _ => {}
                    }
                }
                None => {}
            }

            i = i + 1u64
        }

        result
    }

    // 패키지 정보 조회
    fn get_package_info(ref self, package_id: PackageID) -> Option<(PackageName, Version, string, u64)> {
        let mut i = 0u64

        while i < self.packages.len() {
            let pkg = self.packages.get(i)

            match pkg {
                Some(p) => {
                    if p.id == package_id {
                        let status_str = match p.status {
                            PackageStatus::Available => "available",
                            PackageStatus::Installed => "installed",
                            PackageStatus::Outdated => "outdated",
                            PackageStatus::Broken => "broken"
                        }

                        return Some((p.name, p.version, status_str, p.size))
                    }
                }
                None => {}
            }

            i = i + 1u64
        }

        None
    }

    // 버전 업그레이드
    fn upgrade(mut self, package_id: PackageID, new_version: Version) -> (PackageManager, bool) {
        let mut found = false
        let mut i = 0u64

        while i < self.packages.len() {
            let pkg = self.packages.get(i)

            match pkg {
                Some(p) => {
                    if p.id == package_id && p.status == PackageStatus::Installed {
                        let updated = Package {
                            id: p.id,
                            name: p.name,
                            version: new_version,
                            status: PackageStatus::Installed,
                            installed_at: p.installed_at,
                            size: p.size
                        }
                        self.packages.set(i, updated)
                        found = true
                    }
                }
                None => {}
            }

            i = i + 1u64
        }

        (self, found)
    }

    // 설치된 패키지 수
    fn installed_count(ref self) -> u64 {
        self.installed_packages.len()
    }

    // 전체 설치 크기
    fn total_size(ref self) -> u64 {
        self.total_installed_size
    }

    // 저장소의 패키지 수
    fn available_count(ref self) -> u64 {
        let mut count = 0u64
        let mut i = 0u64

        while i < self.packages.len() {
            let pkg = self.packages.get(i)

            match pkg {
                Some(p) => {
                    match p.status {
                        PackageStatus::Available => {
                            count = count + 1u64
                        }
                        _ => {}
                    }
                }
                None => {}
            }

            i = i + 1u64
        }

        count
    }
}

// === Option 타입 ===

type Option<T> {
    Some(T)
    None
}

// === 유틸리티 ===

fn get_timestamp() -> Timestamp {
    12345678u64
}

// === 테스트 ===

fn main() {
    println!("=== python Phase 1: 패키지 관리 ===")

    let mut pm = PackageManager::new()
    println!("📦 패키지 매니저 초기화")

    // 패키지 저장소에 등록
    println!("\n📝 저장소에 패키지 등록:")
    let (pm2, pkg_numpy) = pm.register_package("numpy", "1.24.0", 52428800u64)
    pm = pm2
    println!("✅ numpy 1.24.0 (50MB)")

    let (pm2, pkg_pandas) = pm.register_package("pandas", "2.0.0", 83886080u64)
    pm = pm2
    println!("✅ pandas 2.0.0 (80MB)")

    let (pm2, pkg_requests) = pm.register_package("requests", "2.31.0", 4194304u64)
    pm = pm2
    println!("✅ requests 2.31.0 (4MB)")

    let (pm2, pkg_flask) = pm.register_package("flask", "2.3.0", 10485760u64)
    pm = pm2
    println!("✅ flask 2.3.0 (10MB)")

    let (pm2, pkg_django) = pm.register_package("django", "4.2.0", 31457280u64)
    pm = pm2
    println!("✅ django 4.2.0 (30MB)")

    // 패키지 설치
    println!("\n📥 패키지 설치:")
    let (pm2, success) = pm.install(pkg_numpy)
    pm = pm2
    println!("✅ numpy 설치 - " ++ (if success { "성공" } else { "실패" }))

    let (pm2, success) = pm.install(pkg_pandas)
    pm = pm2
    println!("✅ pandas 설치 - " ++ (if success { "성공" } else { "실패" }))

    let (pm2, success) = pm.install(pkg_requests)
    pm = pm2
    println!("✅ requests 설치 - " ++ (if success { "성공" } else { "실패" }))

    // 설치된 패키지 목록
    println!("\n📋 설치된 패키지:")
    let installed = pm.list_installed()
    let mut i = 0u64
    while i < installed.len() {
        let (id, name, version) = installed.get(i).unwrap()
        println!("  " ++ name ++ " " ++ version)
        i = i + 1u64
    }

    // 사용 가능한 패키지 목록
    println!("\n🔍 사용 가능한 패키지:")
    let available = pm.list_available()
    let mut i = 0u64
    while i < available.len() {
        let (id, name, version) = available.get(i).unwrap()
        println!("  " ++ name ++ " " ++ version)
        i = i + 1u64
    }

    // 패키지 정보
    println!("\n ℹ️  패키지 정보 (numpy):")
    let info = pm.get_package_info(pkg_numpy)
    match info {
        Some((name, version, status, size)) => {
            println!("  이름: " ++ name)
            println!("  버전: " ++ version)
            println!("  상태: " ++ status)
            println!("  크기: " ++ size.to_string() ++ " bytes")
        }
        None => {}
    }

    // 버전 업그레이드
    println!("\n🔄 버전 업그레이드:")
    let (pm2, success) = pm.upgrade(pkg_numpy, "1.25.0")
    pm = pm2
    println!("✅ numpy 1.25.0으로 업그레이드 - " ++ (if success { "성공" } else { "실패" }))

    // 통계
    println!("\n📊 통계:")
    let installed_count = pm.installed_count()
    let available_count = pm.available_count()
    let total_size = pm.total_size()
    println!("  설치됨: " ++ installed_count.to_string())
    println!("  사용 가능: " ++ available_count.to_string())
    println!("  총 크기: " ++ total_size.to_string() ++ " bytes")
}
